   <br>
For the last two weeks I had found it hard to get groups. Only 2 out of 5 days I would get invited to one. Now, before that I had been on a 2-3 month break from EQ so I didn't think there was actually a problem since I was only going to be playing a few hours after school. After this nite I'm in deep thought in whether people are finding it harder to get groups, wizards aren't wanted (xcept the uber ones), or is it just me stinking up the place with my char.<br>
   <br>
Any input from anyone would be very much appreciated. I don't know what I'm doing anymore or what I should be doing to get myself back on track. All I know is is that I am unguilded, poor, and can't get a group for my life so that I can finaly reach the needed req to enter a guild.<br>
<br>
