My suggestion to you is to join a guild that raids, but where you would be one of the higher level people at lvl 61. Look for a guild that targets Kael/Skyshrine/Halls of testing as raid targets. Since you'll be one of the higher level people, you'll probably get a lot of group invites from within the guild for PoN/PoI/PoD groups while at the same time getting some raid experience under your belt. After awhile of this, you should be lvl 65, have a few nice AA skills and have upgraded your gear a bit. At that point perhaps you could get to know some of the members of a more accomplished guild, get in good with them(be yourself though) and then when the time is right, apply for membership. Then ride their coattails to the Plane of Time and a leet magelo<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
